  "title": "Account cum Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p>•\tEnter transactions accurately into accounting systems (e.g., QuickBooks).</p><p>•\tAssist with month-end closing and financial reporting and reconciliation.</p><p>•\tHandling Petty Cash</p><p>•\tManage day-to-day office operations, including maintaining office stationery, equipment and facilities.</p><p>•\tTo maintain and assist in all company inventories such as salon, spa and office.</p><p>•\tPreparation, maintaining, filing the documents, vouchers, including employment contracts, offer contracts and other office operation and finance related materials</p><p>•\tAdminister leave, attendance and claim ensuring accurate and timely processing (Knowledge in Infotech is advantageous)</p><p>•\tAny ad hoc duties assigned.</p><p>Key Skills & Qualifications</p><p>•\tMeticulous, organized, and detail oriented.</p><p>•\tGood command of English and communication skills.</p><p>•\tProficiency in MS Office (especially Excel) and accounting software.</p><p>•\tAbility to work independently and as part of a team.</p><p>•\tRelevant experience work pass application/ cancellation process.</p><p>•\tBasic knowledge of accounting principles and bookkeeping.<br /></p><p>Schedule: Monday-Friday 9am to 6pm.<br /><br />Singaporean and PR only.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. Kindly send your resume at operations@lasource.com.sg or whatsapp +6597118707.</p>",
